data.description: Welcome to 2401 Spirit Dancer Dr., a meticulously maintained haven nestled in the Walker Place Subdivision of Copperas Cove. This beautiful house stands proudly on a corner lot, boasting a fusion of comfort, convenience, and contemporary living. This inviting four-bedroom home, complemented by a bonus room, effortlessly combines a seamless blend of spaciousness and comfort. Upon entry, you're welcomed into a tranquil space where every detail reflects a sense of warmth and care. The primary bedroom, conveniently located on the main floor, ensures privacy and convenience. Inside, pristine interiors offer a haven for relaxation, while outside, the well-appointed backyard beckons for leisure and entertainment. A playground awaits playful moments and a charming fire pit invites cozy gatherings under the night sky. Recent updates include a new back fence and roof replaced in 2022, ensuring both security and aesthetic appeal. Additionally, the open kitchen offers stainless steel appliances enhancing its functionality and modern appeal. This property is approximately 6 miles away from major grocery stores, 10 miles from Clear Creek Army Entrance, and 13 miles from TJ Mills Army Entrance. Don't miss the opportunity to visit this home. Schedule your viewing today and immerse yourself in the essence of effortless living in Copperas Cove.
